Schedule Webex Meetings from a mobile device
If you have a Webex host account, you can schedule meetings using your mobile device.
iOS
Android
1
Open the Meetings app and swipe left to My Meetings.
2
Tap Schedule , and then enter your meeting info:
Meeting topic
Meeting date, start time, and duration
Meeting password
Inviteesâ€“allow the app to access your contacts on your device or manually enter participant emails and tap Return to add them to your participant list.
3
Review your meeting details and then tap Schedule to schedule your meeting.

  If your meeting is within the next 15 minutes, tap Start instead.